{
  "texts": [
    "• 68.7% (2,549 respondents) would not recommend the profession of a professional driver to family or acquaintances, while 31.3% (1,159 respondents) would recommend it (Q46).",
    "• Responding to the question, \"What grade would you generally give to the professional driver's profession?, \" the mean grade provided by respondents was 6.27 out of 10 (Q56).",
    "The most common grade was 7 (n = 1,006).",
    "• Finally, the majority of the respondents have a neutral to slightly negative outlook on the future, with a mean of 4.48 on a scale of 1 (Very negative) to 10 (Very positive) (Q64).",
    "The most frequently selected grade was 5 (n = 770)."
  ]
}